---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("October 19 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="When to Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning"
  description={isPublished ? "Full Article: How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?" : "Coming Soon: How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?"}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?"
    description={isPublished ? "Read our full guide to How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?" : "Coming Soon: How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?"}
    publishDate="October 19 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Urgency/Direct Response
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming October 19 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>October 19 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>How Early Should I Book a Pre-Holiday House Cleaning?</h2>
<p><strong>For a stress-free holiday season, booking your pre-holiday house cleaning at least 4 to 6 weeks in advance is crucial. The demand for professional cleaning services in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas spikes as the holidays approach, and early booking ensures your home is pristine and ready for festive gatherings.</strong></p>

<h3>Why Schedule Early?</h3>
<p>Booking your pre-holiday cleaning early guarantees that you lock in a spot during the busiest time of the year. Our trained cleaning specialists at The Valley Clean Team are in high demand, especially from November through December. Here's why you should act now:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>High Demand:</strong> The holiday season sees a surge in cleaning requests, leaving last-minute bookings at risk of disappointment.</li>
  <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Secure your cleaning appointment early to avoid the stress of scrambling to prepare your home for guests.</li>
  <li><strong>Flexible Scheduling:</strong> Early bookings allow you to choose the most convenient time slots that fit your schedule.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Understanding the Holiday Rush in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas</h3>
<p>The Shoals & Surrounding Areas are bustling with holiday activities, making it a vibrant yet hectic time. From festive parades to family gatherings, your schedule can fill up quickly. A pre-holiday cleaning ensures your home is ready for:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Entertaining Guests:</strong> Your home will be spotless and welcoming for family and friends.</li>
  <li><strong>Holiday Decorations:</strong> A clean slate allows for the perfect backdrop for your festive decor.</li>
  <li><strong>Seasonal Events:</strong> With a clean home, you can focus on enjoying local festivities without worrying about chores.</li>
</ul>

<h3>What to Expect from Our Pre-Holiday Cleaning Service</h3>
<p>At The Valley Clean Team, our pre-holiday cleaning service is designed to meet the highest standards. Our systematic approach includes:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Thorough Cleaning:</strong> From baseboards to ceiling fans, every corner is meticulously cleaned.</li>
  <li><strong>Customized Plans:</strong> Tailored cleaning options to match your specific needs and preferences.</li>
  <li><strong>Guaranteed Satisfaction:</strong> Our military-precision checklists ensure a perfect clean every time.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Transparent Pricing and No Surprises</h4>
<p>We believe in transparency and upfront pricing. Our services start at $125, and we provide a detailed quote so you know exactly what to expect. No hidden fees, just exceptional service.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Holiday Season: Book Your Cleaning Today</h3>
<p>Don't let the holiday rush catch you off guard. Reclaim your time and enjoy the festive season with a pristine home. Book your pre-holiday house cleaning with The Valley Clean Team today. Our vetted specialists are ready to deliver a guaranteed, spotless clean. <strong>See availability and get your free quote now.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">October 19 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
